## Automatic: human-todos → Linear

**When adding a new checklist item to `src/docs/human-todos.md`, automatically:**
1. Create a corresponding Linear issue using the prefix convention above
2. Use `LDW-DEV-WEB` for dev tasks on the website, `LDW-BIZ` for strategy/content
3. Include the Linear issue ID in the human-todos item (e.g. `- [ ] **A-100** Set up cookie consent…`)
4. Add the issue to the "Linear Issues Created" list at the top of human-todos.md if that section exists

**Example:** Adding "Set up cookie consent management" → create `LDW-DEV-WEB Set up cookie consent management` in Linear, then reference `A-100` (or the returned ID) in human-todos.

